  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess efficacy, as determined by the proportion of subjects
      with Sustained Virologic Response at Post-Treatment Week 12 (SVR12), defined as Hepatitis C
      virus (HCV) Ribonucleic acid (RNA) &lt; Limit of quantitation (LOQ) at post-treatment Week 12.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      -  ASV = Asunaprevir (BMS-650032)

        -  DCV = Daclatasvir (BMS-790052)

        -  Peg = Peg-interferon Alfa-2a (PegIFN)

        -  Rib = Ribavirin (RBV)
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
